window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>Each of Sean's wives takes a moment to share a tale of their past while sitting around having a drink. Contains the Valens Legacy novellas <i>Roxy and Jolene</i> and <i>Daelyn and Roberta</i>.</p> <p><b><i>Roxy and Jolene</i></b></p> <p>Roxy explains just what happened back in Las Vegas that caused her father to have such animosity towards Sawyer. Jolene tells of the events that led to her decision to become a tantric witch.</p> <p><b><i>Daelyn and Roberta</i></b></p> <p>Daelyn tells of the events that led up to her owning her car. Roberta recounts her experiences with Sampson and how her daughter came to be.</p> <p><b>Warning: Contains mature content.</b></p>"; 
